On the evening of February 17, in Shangli, Jiangxi Province, during a drunk driving inspection, a man driving under the influence without a license stabbed two police officers and an auxiliary police officer with a knife. The three died after failed rescue efforts.
If I remember correctly, this should be the fifth knife murder case in recent days.

The 23-year-old internet celebrity "Egg Princess" was cyberbullied because of her pink hair in a photo she posted on her personal social media when she visited her grandfather. She eventually committed suicide due to depression.
It is reported that she was born in 1999 and had excellent academic performance. Not long ago, she was recommended to graduate school. She took the admission letter to surprise her 84-year-old grandfather on the hospital bed, but encountered malicious cyberbullying in the comment section.
